name: Red 5 (V)
Lore: 'Luke''s Incom T-65 X-wing at the Battle of Yavin. Instrumentation similarities between Red 5 and the T-16 skyhopper allowed Luke to play a pivotal role in the conflict.',
Text: 'May add Luke as pilot and [A New Hope] R2-D2 (may deploy here from Reserve Deck; reshuffle). During battle, may cancel a starfighter''s game text here (except related to capacity, ability, and identity of permanent pilot). Immune to attrition < 6.',
